</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><p>走到if的时候，会先执行<code v-pre>refCount.decrementAndGet()</code>方法减1，如果是0，将减一后的值赋值给自己。</p>
<figure><img src="@source/杂记/AtomicInteger的用法/images/image-20230505153523675.png" alt="image-20230505153523675" tabindex="0" loading="lazy"><figcaption>image-20230505153523675</figcaption></figure>
<p>这个对象高频的创建，就使用了commons-pool2对象池,刚好这个对象要被四个线程使用，所有就用了这个引用计数</p>
